#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Nakulapituvagga "
msgstr "1. Nakula’s Father "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Dutiyaupādāparitassanāsutta "
msgstr "8. Anxiety Because of Grasping (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.8:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.8:1.2"
msgid "“Upādāparitassanañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi anupādāaparitassanañca. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you how grasping leads to anxiety, and how not grasping leads to freedom from anxiety. "

msgctxt "sn22.8:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha … pe … "
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention, I will speak. "

msgctxt "sn22.8:1.4"
msgid "kathañca, bhikkhave, upādāparitassanā hoti? "
msgstr "And how does grasping lead to anxiety? "

msgctxt "sn22.8:1.5"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, assutavā puthujjano rūpaṃ ‘etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’ti samanupassati. "
msgstr "It’s when an uneducated ordinary person regards form like this: ‘This is mine, I am this, this is my self.’ "

msgctxt "sn22.8:1.6"
msgid "Tassa taṃ rūpaṃ vipariṇamati aññathā hoti. "
msgstr "But that form of theirs decays and perishes, "

msgctxt "sn22.8:1.7"
msgid "Tassa rūpavipariṇāmaññathābhāvā uppajjanti sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsā. "
msgstr "which gives rise to sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress. "

msgctxt "sn22.8:1.8"
msgid "Vedanaṃ etaṃ mama … pe … "
msgstr "They regard feeling … "

msgctxt "sn22.8:1.9"
msgid "saññaṃ etaṃ mama … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn22.8:1.10"
msgid "saṅkhāre etaṃ mama … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn22.8:1.11"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ ‘etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’ti samanupassati. "
msgstr "consciousness like this: ‘This is mine, I am this, this is my self.’ "

msgctxt "sn22.8:1.12"
msgid "Tassa taṃ viññāṇaṃ vipariṇamati aññathā hoti. "
msgstr "But that consciousness of theirs decays and perishes, "

msgctxt "sn22.8:1.13"
msgid "Tassa viññāṇavipariṇāmaññathābhāvā uppajjanti sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsā. "
msgstr "which gives rise to sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress. "

msgctxt "sn22.8:1.14"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, upādāparitassanā hoti. "
msgstr "That’s how grasping leads to anxiety. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.19, sc2
msgctxt "sn22.8:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, anupādāaparitassanā hoti? "
msgstr "And how does not grasping lead to freedom from anxiety? "

msgctxt "sn22.8:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpaṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti samanupassati. "
msgstr "It’s when an educated noble disciple regards form like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’ "

msgctxt "sn22.8:2.3"
msgid "Tassa taṃ rūpaṃ vipariṇamati aññathā hoti. "
msgstr "When that form of theirs decays and perishes, "

msgctxt "sn22.8:2.4"
msgid "Tassa rūpavipariṇāmaññathābhāvā nuppajjanti sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsā. "
msgstr "it doesn’t give rise to sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress. "

msgctxt "sn22.8:2.5"
msgid "Vedanaṃ netaṃ mama … "
msgstr "They regard feeling … "

msgctxt "sn22.8:2.6"
msgid "saññaṃ netaṃ mama … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn22.8:2.7"
msgid "saṅkhāre netaṃ mama … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn22.8:2.8"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti samanupassati. "
msgstr "consciousness like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’ "

msgctxt "sn22.8:2.9"
msgid "Tassa taṃ viññāṇaṃ vipariṇamati aññathā hoti. "
msgstr "When that consciousness of theirs decays and perishes, "

msgctxt "sn22.8:2.10"
msgid "Tassa viññāṇavipariṇāmaññathābhāvā nuppajjanti sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsā. "
msgstr "it doesn’t give rise to sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress. "

msgctxt "sn22.8:2.11"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, anupādāaparitassanā hotī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how not grasping leads to freedom from anxiety.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.8:2.12"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

